                                В В В 	WHEREAS it is expedient to make provisions to give effect to the financial proposals of the Government and to amend certain laws for the purpose hereinafter appearing;В В В В 	NOW, THEREFORE, in pursuance of the Proclamation of the 24th March, 1982, and in exercise of all powers enabling him on that behalf, the Chief Martial Law Administrator is pleased to make and promulgate the following Ordinance:-

